{"TopicId":159903,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Blue Origin thread.","CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-28T21:34:49Z","PageNum":63,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T15:32:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo how long until this thing is flying daily?\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty exciting that they are getting ready to carry people!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:03:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2283826381\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1382362117211189253?s=20\u0022 style=\u0022height:509px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:05:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWen hop\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003EI think I\u0027m overusing this joke, help\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:12:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe hold they are in now is longer than the entire flight I think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:15:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022brief hold\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GuessingEveryDay","CreatedById":203507,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:26:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanwhile the SpaceX fans are storming the YouTube chat. Man... I\u0027m a SpaceX fanboy, but not that much!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:awe:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/awe.png\u0022 title=\u0022:awe:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Terminal Velocity","CreatedById":209328,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:27:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBlue moon lander for ksp as a mod possibly please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso why the heck is the hold 30 minutes long (But they did hold for 45 minutes on NS-14 so maybe same deal?) Anyways, NEW SHEPARD STEAKOUT\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:30:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223954341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618417577\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203507\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GuessingEveryDay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, GuessingEveryDay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanwhile the SpaceX fans are storming the YouTube chat. Man... I\u0027m a SpaceX fanboy, but not that much!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:awe:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/awe.png\u0022 title=\u0022:awe:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t they disable chat? I\u0027m not seeing it on my stream.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:31:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223954347\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618417814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t they disable chat? I\u0027m not seeing it on my stream.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s disabled on the official one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:37:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is no chat, never is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T16:39:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOut of hold now, New Shepard high-altitude flight test in 10 mins \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-14T16:40:06Z\u0022 title=\u002204/14/2021 04:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 14, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by RealKerbal3x\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T17:01:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood launch and landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T17:01:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027ve got to get the price competing with parabolic airplane rides.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T17:04:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent drone shots on this one!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GuessingEveryDay","CreatedById":203507,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T17:12:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223954344\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618417656\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209328\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocketry101\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, Rocketry101 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBlue moon lander for ksp as a mod possibly please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry bud, this is the wrong place to ask.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T17:16:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it\u0027s just that this is a much smaller rocket with lots of extra mass fraction to play around with but it is SPORTY off the pad. Makes an Atlas V or a Falcon 9 look positively sluggish.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RCgothic","CreatedById":132560,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T20:25:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s easy for shorter rockets to look quick. The same speed is more body-lengths which is how we tend to judge speediness.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-14T21:54:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7335114630\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://twitter.com/blueorigin/status/1382451440661061634?s=20\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T13:46:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/tGw-hN8hKXw?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou go to their website so you can sign up to learn how to buy the first seat in a few days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not just tell people what it costs? How is it hype to wait days to find out? I guess if you have so much money it doesn\u0027t matter what it costs this video is for you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikegarrison","CreatedById":137807,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T17:20:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you have to ask how much it costs, you can\u0027t afford it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikegarrison","CreatedById":137807,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T18:01:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact ... let\u0027s think about who is trying to sell space tourism.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nJeff Bezos, richest guy in the world.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nElon Musk, also at times richest guy in the world.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nRichard Branson, pretty rich guy also.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it ever seem like maybe their idea of what would be an affordable lark might be a little distorted?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CatastrophicFailure","CreatedById":57438,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T18:13:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223963164\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619719286\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mikegarrison\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, mikegarrison said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact ... let\u0027s think about who is trying to sell space tourism.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nJeff Bezos, richest guy in the world.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nElon Musk, also at times richest guy in the world.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nRichard Branson, pretty rich guy also.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it ever seem like maybe their idea of what would be an affordable lark might be a little distorted?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGee, if only their plans didn\u2019t also incorporate hundreds of other people in order to work at all, some of whom may be there specifically to proffer economic reality checks about potential market sizes...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk that came out a bit snarky, but seriously, these guys don\u2019t run their operations in a vacuum. They have \u003Cem\u003Epeople\u003C/em\u003E to tell them where that merge between \u201Caffordable\u201D and \u201Cactually funds the operation\u201D is.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikegarrison","CreatedById":137807,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T18:18:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223963169\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619720024\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257438\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CatastrophicFailure\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, CatastrophicFailure said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGee, if only their plans didn\u2019t also incorporate hundreds of other people in order to work at all, some of whom may be there specifically to proffer economic reality checks about potential market sizes...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk that came out a bit snarky, but seriously, these guys don\u2019t run their operations in a vacuum. They have \u003Cem\u003Epeople\u003C/em\u003E to tell them where that merge between \u201Caffordable\u201D and \u201Cactually funds the operation\u201D is.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you seriously trying to argue that space tourism isn\u0027t exclusively for the super-rich?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe don\u0027t know for sure yet what a ticket on New Shepard costs, but we know Virgin Galactic is pricing theirs at $250,000 for a flight. And that\u0027s supposedly a discounted \u0022early adopter\u0022 price.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-29T18:28:25Z\u0022 title=\u002204/29/2021 06:28  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 29, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by mikegarrison\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T18:20:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223963164\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619719286\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mikegarrison\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, mikegarrison said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it ever seem like maybe their idea of what would be an affordable lark might be a little distorted?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCertainly true. That said, if they could fly NS for 10s of thousands a seat instead of 100s, they might actually broaden the market substantially.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know people who have been saving up to try Everest, for example. Not poor by any stretch, but not \u003Cem\u003Erich\u003C/em\u003E, either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n(wanna say it\u0027s on the order of 50k)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flying dutchman","CreatedById":189896,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-29T18:20:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGoing on holliday by plane was also only for the super rich at first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}